Package net.metro.analyze

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MarkerListener
    Interface designed to inform other GUI elements of actions taken place within a SystemMap.
    PointListener
    Interface designed to inform other GUI elements of actions taken place within a SystemMap.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddRoutePath
    Frame that allows the user to select a RoutePath to add to the route path constraint.
    DataControlPalette
    This internal frame is the controller for all data visualizations on the map.
    Driver
    The driver class for the application.
    FileExport
    Abstract class for exporting data edited from within MASS.
    FileImport
    Abstract class for importing data to be used within MASS.
    LineEdit
    Frame that allows for the editing of route data including the route numbers, route paths, and route waypoints and stops.
    MainFrame
    Extends the functionality of the MapFrame class by adding the ability to manipulate existing data from within the SystemObjects database.
    MapFrame
    Main controller for MASS.
    MarkerListener.MarkerEvent
    Event object containing information regarding changes to map WayPoints and Stops.
    MetroMapController
    Extends the functionality of the DefaultMapController class by adding functionality specific to MASS.
    PointListener.PointEvent
    Event object containing information regarding selection of a point on a SystemMap.
    RouteEdit
    Dialog that assists in editing Route information including name and number.
    RouteExport
    Extension of the FileExport class designed to export existing route data from within MASS to an external .csv file.
    RouteImport
    Extends the FileImport class designed to import Routes from an external .csv file into MASS.
    RoutePathEdit
    Dialog that assists in editing RoutePath information including route path name and route path id.
    SelectStop
    Dialog that appears when multiple stops are found near the clicked point.
    ServiceImport
    Extends the FileImport class designed to import Services from an external .csv file into MASS.
    SystemMap
    The hub for everything map-related in MASS.
    WayPointEdit
    Dialog that assists in editing WayPoint information including the type of waypoint (WayPoint or Stop), the location, and if a stop, the stop's name and id.
